            <description><![CDATA[【“能吃是福”？男孩120斤“胖”出胰腺炎，吓得我筷子都掉了！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[抓狂]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_zhuakuang-c007ffb7fe.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】“爸爸也胖，高血脂，他们家就没有瘦人。”面对医生的问询，妈妈略表惆怅和担心。11岁男孩腹痛难忍、持续性呕吐，还发低烧，到医院一查：坏死性胰腺炎。好巧不巧，爸爸也是胰腺炎，两人同一天住进医院。肥胖、高血脂易引发胰腺炎，胰腺炎久了，会发展成“癌中之王”——胰腺癌。害怕？那就尽早预防：1.不要太胖；2.不暴饮暴食；3.少烟酒；4.定期体检👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%97%AA%E9%97%AA%E7%9A%84%E5%84%BF%E7%A7%91%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%97%AA%E9%97%AA%E7%9A%84%E5%84%BF%E7%A7%91%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#闪闪的儿科医生#</span></a> <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4910390988177424" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">深圳卫健委的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/a8bfee30gy1her33bfzvuj21hc0u07bp.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/NtI1tgWngx08653LxQH601041200LGI30E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1686287935&amp;ssig=VzU%2BhJ6iI7&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/Mrz7GKdQgx08653L4fSw01041200pZD00E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1686287935&amp;ssig=PJGhyBIO06&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/wmX8Mg5Jgx08653KGHs401041200gQ5q0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1686287935&amp;ssig=l3EUyTVR4Y&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4910390988177424&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target=